Sentencas: This paper presents the results on the development of microtubular solid oxide fuel cells (MT SOFC).
Titulo: Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Elements: Development and Testing

Sentencas: A review of the literature data on solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC) is also presented.
Titulo: Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Elements: Development and Testing

Sentencas: The procedure of MT SOFCs manufacture by means of the phase inversion technique and characterization methods are described.
Titulo: Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Elements: Development and Testing

Sentencas: A measuring cell to determine the current-voltage characteristics of MT SOFC is described.
Titulo: Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Elements: Development and Testing

Sentencas: The obtained data allow us to outline further routes to increase the capacity of MT SOFCs.
Titulo: Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Elements: Development and Testing
